Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,became the final confirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:33.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When Kira defeated Kibune,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.83,0:01:38.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Genryusai acquired the Bakkouto,\Nthe proof of Kumoi's treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.41,0:01:41.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Genryusai then ordered\Nthe Thirteen Court Guard Squads
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.11,0:01:43.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to storm\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:47.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumoi ordered his subordinate assassins\Nto hold off the attack
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:49.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,as he attempted to escape\Ninto a facility protected by a barrier,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:52.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but he was stopped\Nby Yoruichi's efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.45,0:01:57.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Cornered, Kumoi tried to barricade\Nhimself in the tower
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:01:59.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,by using Rurichiyo as his hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:03.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:11.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagai…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.16,0:02:25.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:29.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:30.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You did a good job…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:34.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Substitute Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:37.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that…\Nsupposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:45.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.88,0:02:47.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.28,0:02:52.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:04.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did he do just now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:06.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have never seen such a Kido.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:09.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely a special technique\Nused to relocate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:11.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,while completely suppressing\None's Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:12.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That means…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:14.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I hate to admit it, but there is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.93,0:03:16.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,no way for us to pursue him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.20,0:03:19.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not an option!\NHe has Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:39.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Amagai?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:49.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here out of the blue
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.10,0:03:51.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,with the Kasumiohji Clan's princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.24,0:03:53.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,State your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.68,0:03:56.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:00.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.56,0:04:03.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably never\Neven dreamed that
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:07.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,someone in Soul Society\Nwould be coming to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:13.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me? For what reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:15.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinetsu Kisaragi…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.52,0:04:18.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisaragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:22.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you haven't forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:26.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have come from hell on
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.65,0:04:29.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinetsu Kisaragi's behalf to defeat you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:31.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bloom in glory,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.40,0:04:33.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Benishidare!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:42.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had completely\Nsuppressed my Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.08,0:04:45.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what I would expect\Nfrom the princess's guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.80,0:04:47.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But your resistance\Nis meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:51.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence! Benishidare, Sange!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.04,0:05:01.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:04.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:11.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shake, Daichimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:24.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:30.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:32.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:35.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're safe now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.08,0:05:37.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.00,0:05:39.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Enryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.21,0:05:41.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So that is what\Nyour voice sounds like!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:46.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not be embarrassed!\NIt is a fine voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:49.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Princess!\NWe must move now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:51.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenryu! Enryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.87,0:06:17.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagai… What do you\Nintend on doing with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:19.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:26.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the core of the Bakkouto.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:30.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The battles up until now\Nwere for the purpose of
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:33.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,allowing this core to absorb\Nthe Spiritual Pressure of the strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.38,0:06:39.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And now,\Nwhen I feed this to my Bakkouto…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:46.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it will display it's true power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:03.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what you were up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.96,0:07:06.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You were after the Bakkouto as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.43,0:07:08.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.16,0:07:13.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:21.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Render all things in\Nthe universe to ashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.33,0:07:36.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryujinjakka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.20,0:07:40.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself,\NShusuke Amagai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:59.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you…\NWhat have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:07.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The ability to cancel out\Nthe power of Soul Reapers…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.11,0:08:10.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the power of my Bakkouto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:16.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as this Bakkouto is active,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:19.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,all Zanpakuto are useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.37,0:08:21.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All except for…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.64,0:08:26.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,my Raika.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:31.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai! Raika Gouenkaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:21.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the two of you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:23.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:29.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:34.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that look in your eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:37.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to kill you first?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:38.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.88,0:09:43.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought your beef was with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:47.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Those people have\Nnothing to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:51.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing to do with it?\NYou're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:55.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not the only one\NI am after!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:58.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I will kill the heir to\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.64,0:10:02.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,along with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:05.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:11.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.48,0:10:15.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I took so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:23.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you…find us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.80,0:10:26.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kenryu left behind\Na Hell Butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:30.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So it made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:34.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man!\NWhy aren't you fighting back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.96,0:10:41.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he can't,\Neven if he wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.96,0:10:45.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My Bakkouto cancels out\Nthe power of Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:46.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:50.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Genryusai's flames\Nhave no effect on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:57.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagai…\NI don't want to believe it, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:00.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you our enemy, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:03.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:20.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Byakuya, are you done here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:23.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The lieutenants are mopping up\Nthe remaining enemy forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:25.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How's your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:28.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We have taken control of\Nthe Bakkouto workshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:31.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Soi Fon is preserving\Nthe site as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.00,0:11:35.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly,\Nwhere is Shusuke Amagai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:36.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:38.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He entered the grounds when
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:41.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Madarame and others first stormed in,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:42.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but I haven't seen him since.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.47,0:11:44.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:47.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Something happened to Amagai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.32,0:11:51.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the true mastermind\Nbehind this commotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.49,0:11:53.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:57.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At Urahara's request,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.64,0:12:00.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking into the on-going confusion
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:02.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,regarding the logistics of Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:05.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In the process,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:07.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I came across the cleverly hidden
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:10.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,secret of the Kasumiohji Clan's dark side.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:19.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyokaku Kumoi was the first\Nto create a Bakkouto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:21.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He developed the weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:24.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,by applying techniques used to create
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.73,0:12:26.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,goods for the royal family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:29.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Bakkouto is a weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:31.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that forces its wielder to display abilities beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.51,0:12:33.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that which the wielder possesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:36.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The resulting toll,\Nhowever, is huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.92,0:12:38.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:41.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagai learned of the existence of the Bakkouto,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:45.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but he approached Kumoi\Nin order to get his hands on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:48.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And he was moving forward
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:52.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,with some sort of grand scheme\Nusing the Bakkouto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:55.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,To that end, he needed to become\Na Squad Captain in order to
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.24,0:12:56.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,gain a grasp of the movements of
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:59.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,both the Soul Reapers and Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.15,0:13:00.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:05.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Amagai, who became
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:07.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,a captain in order to carry out his plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.58,0:13:08.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,began making his move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:11.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,With regard to the fact that the shutdown\Nrequest for the Restrictive Current
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:13.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,didn't properly go through\Nshortly after he made captain…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:16.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He discreetly\Nvoided that request,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.64,0:13:19.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,allowing him to show off his powers\Nto his squad and win their support.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:23.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he approached\Nthe other captains to gain their trust,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.64,0:13:25.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and advocated cooperation between other
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.42,0:13:27.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,squads and proposed training exercises.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:29.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, his true purpose was to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:32.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,analyze the fighting ability of each squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.84,0:13:36.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, as he steadily\Nmade preparations,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:39.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,he even took advantage\Nof an unexpected opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.26,0:13:41.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Ichigo Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:43.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:45.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He originally intended to make
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:47.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,his move after much further preparation,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:50.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but Ichigo's intervention\Ncaused confusion in Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:53.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He instigated the ambitious Kumoi
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:55.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and magnified the commotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:58.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,instantly plunging\NSoul Society into chaos
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:02.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,by using the Kasumiohji Clan's\Nassassin squad
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:06.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and Kibune, his Third Seat,\Nwhom he chose himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:09.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a report that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.02,0:14:12.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Kira defeated Third Seat Kibune.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.28,0:14:14.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira did?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.28,0:14:16.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that he defeated Third Seat Kibune
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,became the final confirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:23.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Amagai apparently didn't\Ncalculate on Kira winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:27.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He underestimated\Nthe Thirteen Court Guard Squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:32.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He was willing to go that far?\NTo what end?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:35.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,About that…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:52.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinetsu Kisaragi…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:56.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it that you\Nknow that name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:02.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinetsu Kisaragi…was…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:05.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the name of my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.76,0:15:14.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. My father's name\Nwas Shinetsu Kisaragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:18.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Soul Reaper\Nyou murdered!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.05,0:15:37.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Head Captain…\Nkilled him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.02,0:15:41.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man,\Nis what he's saying true?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.83,0:15:44.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:51.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I killed the Soul Reaper\Nnamed Shinetsu Kisaragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:28.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you find out\Nthat I killed your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:33.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,After you cut him down,\Nmy father was still barely alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:38.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That day,\Nmy father was acting a bit strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:40.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to look for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.02,0:16:44.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:50.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That place was where my father
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.52,0:16:52.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,always trained with his Zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:16:58.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.61,0:17:03.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:04.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.30,0:17:06.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:07.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:09.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please open your eyes!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:10.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:13.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Father was down to his dying breath,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:15.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but he said it clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.88,0:17:19.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That you cut him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:21.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:24.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:29.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:33.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This man killed my father,\Nhis subordinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.25,0:17:43.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Several years after\Nthe death of my father…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:47.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I changed my name and enlisted
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.03,0:17:48.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in the Thirteen Court Guard Squads
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:50.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,claiming I was from\Nthe Rukon district.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:55.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it to investigate the truth\Nabout my father's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.35,0:17:59.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I gathered information.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:03.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And then I realized…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,"Bakkouto."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.66,0:18:12.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the last word\Nmy father said!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:15.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What was a Bakkouto?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:18.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did my father say that word?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.31,0:18:22.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It took many years,\Nbut I gradually came to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.34,0:18:27.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My father somehow came to stumble
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.43,0:18:29.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,upon the existence of the Bakkouto
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.14,0:18:32.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and was apparently delving\Ninto its mysteries by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:37.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, in order to find out the truth about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.17,0:18:39.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,he infiltrated the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:41.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:51.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In those days,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:52.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you worked in collusion with the Kasumiohji Clan
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:55.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and were involved in\Nthe development of the Bakkouto.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:58.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My father grasped proof of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:00.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why you…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:04.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,silenced him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:08.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:12.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,even if there were suspicious activities in the Kasumiohji Clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.62,0:19:16.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you refused to intervene until now\Nusing immunity as your reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:23.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.90,0:19:27.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I swore revenge against you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:32.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Defeating you was my only thought
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:35.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,as I spent the years training myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:40.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I approached the Kasumiohji Clan
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.58,0:19:42.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and obtained the Bakkouto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:45.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I distinguished myself\Nwith the Expedition Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:50.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally making it as a captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:51.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I waited for my time of opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:58.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is the time for me to\Ntake my revenge for my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.34,0:20:12.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.62,0:20:16.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo Kasumiohji's fiancé,\NShu Kannogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.66,0:20:20.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You are Soul Reaper Squad Captains,\Nare you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:22.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.10,0:20:24.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.22,0:20:27.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help Ichigo\Nand the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:29.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:31.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo and the others
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:35.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,followed Ruricchi and \NCaptain Amagai to the Head Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:44.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Out of my way, Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:46.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:48.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been listening to you\Nall this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.12,0:20:50.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard.\NThat was nothing but selfish babble!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.45,0:20:54.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I just told the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:58.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not talking about whether\Nthat was the truth or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:02.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of your selfish actions…\Nother people were…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.38,0:21:07.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea\Nhow much pain Rurichiyo was in?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.81,0:21:13.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:15.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Her life was targeted\Nover and over,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:17.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and she went through\None terrifying experience after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.90,0:21:20.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to be free,\Nbut there was no time for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:24.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want revenge,\Ndo it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:26.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't involve people who\Nhave nothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:30.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:38.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it, do you?\NMove!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:40.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who doesn't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.99,0:21:42.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want me to move…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.22,0:21:47.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll have to force me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.30,0:23:23.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi, you should've told us\Nyou were here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.68,0:23:25.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:29.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But it suits me to secretly work\Nbehind the scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.75,0:23:31.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.10,0:23:32.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I like seeing the surprised look\Non everyone's faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.99,0:23:33.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.92,0:23:34.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.45,0:23:36.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.17,0:23:40.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Chojiro Sasakibe,\NSquad 1 Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.34,0:23:42.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspired by English gentlemen he saw
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.97,0:23:44.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,long ago in the World of the Living,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.53,0:23:46.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sasakibe tries to\Nmaster his tea hobby
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.64,0:23:51.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,by growing tea leaves in Soul Society\Nand brewing his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.50,0:23:58.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.38,0:24:02.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant,\Nthe Squad Barracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.98,0:24:05.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't me!